data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! This home is quaint, cozy and oh-so-ready to be called home.  Step into the welcoming living that is light and bright featuring hardwood floors and floor to ceiling windows.  The living room flows nicely into the sizable kitchen, complete with plenty of storage which opens to the dining room, making it easy to entertain your family and friends.  The main floor is finished with two large bedrooms and a full bathroom.  The lower level features a second kitchen and dining area, two additional bedrooms, a ÃÂ¾ bathroom and large laundry room that provides the opportunity to rent out the basement and cover a significant amount of your mortgage payment .  Outdoors you'll enjoy a spacious yard with plenty of room to entertain and to play.  You will love living in this neighborhood.  With excellent schools and easy access to shopping, entertainment and anywhere in the valley everything you want is nearby.  This gem has everything you are looking for and more.  Amazing opportunity for an owner occupant or investor. This home would generate immediate cash flow for someone looking for an investment opportunity.
